---
title: Southern Crumbed Chicken Tacos with Charred Corn Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Crispy crumbed chicken, creamy slaw and charred corn in a taco – we promise, this combo is love at first bite!
And second bite, and third bite...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-chicken-tender-tacos-15a5d6b4.jpg
